data.description: PRICE REDUCED! MOTIVATED SELLER! Prime Location in beautiful Starting Point Horse Community near World Equestrian Center and HITS. Expansive 20 acre lot high and dry on curve boosts expansive views. Mature granddaddy oaks throughout property. Well built 3/3 two story stone and block home. Breathtaking vaulted great room with 2 story stone fireplace, beamed ceiling, and 2 story wall of windows. Master suite on first floor with guest quarters on second floor. Large block barn with 14 stalls. Additional center aisle stallion/mare barn with 6 stalls.  Hay area, barn bath, tack room, feed room, riders lounge/could be barn sleeping qrtrs. 5 paddocks/pastures with water, 2 round pens. Would make perfect winter training farm for any discipline.  Access to track.  Priced to sell! Next to million dollar farms!
